---
description: Visual quality and art direction rules for OGDILAC
globs: public/**/*.html, public/css/**/*.css, public/js/**/*.js
alwaysApply: true
---

For all UI work:
- prioritize premium art direction over generic layouts
- improve hierarchy, spacing, composition, and depth
- preserve canonical country-page structure
- use the Framer wireframe as shell/style reference
- aim for a modern institutional IADB/BID-like feel
- keep the UI elegant, data-friendly, and high-trust
- avoid flat, generic, low-contrast, weak visual solutions